{"tid":1895071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國呼籲遊客切勿到美國旅遊","createTime":"2020-02-24T10:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T12:06:01.000Z","uid":73092,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7e83fb9ad122c2137d4e721989425d21c7454f","tid":1895071,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國家文化和旅遊部指，中國遊客在美國受到不公平對待，呼籲遊客切勿前往當地。 <br />\n<br />\n文化和旅遊部在官方網頁發公告，指近期由於美方的過度防疫措施，以及美國國內安全形勢，中國遊客在美國屢次遭到不公平對待，提醒中國遊客切實提高安全防範意識，切勿前往美國旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，美國上月底將中國的旅遊警告級別提升至最高，呼籲國民不要前往中國，又禁止十四天內到過中國的非美國公民入境。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部曾經指摘美方是反應過激過度，不斷製造和散播恐慌。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc335c77e4c76dee064d753b990f0fa9bf8841c","tid":1895071,"uid":37596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"幾時永遠唔到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b8b5177123dc6c8c4e7c75cdc3b6ee272facd2","tid":1895071,"uid":2545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"好羨慕...幾時到香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59247bd631e3b6e27ecf618a9cf3f68e1993355","tid":1895071,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6eef2b8457c52fa5c42d295d8bbc6328e1485e5","tid":1895071,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:33:49.000Z","msg":"惡人先告狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e9a243e5929c7f0a2cd57b0ce0156a7adc34d9